jm.gui.cpn

Interface Images

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AppletImages, ToolkitImages

    public interface Images
    Interface with methods for returning Images representing notes, rests and other stave elements for use with a CPN Stave. This abstraction is mainly used to allow different implementations from loading the Images in different ways. For instance, the ToolkitImages implementation is suitable for applications, while the AppletImages implementation is suitable for use in applets.
    See Also:
    Stave, ToolkitImages, AppletImages
